Simple program for generating (and solving) small puzzles like the board game Ricochet Robots.

The ones that I selected for the party:

+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
| .B. . . . . . |
+-+.............+
| . . . . . .G. |
+...+.......+-+.+
| . | . . . .Y. |
+...+.........+-+
| . . . . . . . |
+.......+-+...+.+
| .*. . | . . | |
+.....+-+.....+.+
| . . . . . . . |
+.....+.........+
| .R. | . . . . |
+.+-+.+.........+
| | . . . . . . |
+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
[[Move(color=BLUE, direction=DOWN), Move(color=RED, direction=LEFT), Move(color=RED, direction=UP), Move(color=GREEN, direction=LEFT), Move(color=GREEN, direction=DOWN)]]


